DEPENDENCIES:

This package depends on rootpy which you will also need to install:

From SourceForge:
git clone git://rootpy.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/rootpy/rootpy

From the ATLAS SVN server:
svn checkout svn+ssh://${USER}@svn.cern.ch/reps/atlasusr/end/rootpy/trunk rootpy

INSTALL:

python setup.py install --prefix=/path/to/install/dir

SETUP:

source /path/to/install/dir/etc/atlastools_setup.[c]sh

(put this in your .bashrc)
